Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.11,0:01:39.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:98119,99537}{\i1}Because I'm your dream girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.08,0:01:42.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:101080,102999}{\i1}If you say it just one more time…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.70,0:01:44.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:103708,104751}{\i1}I…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.62,0:01:48.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:107629,108921}You resemble…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.25,0:01:54.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:110256,114302}You resemble the girl\NI can't stop thinking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.80,0:02:00.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:116804,120808}Mom's Secret!\NA Female Thief's Vengeance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.18,0:02:06.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:123186,126564}{\i1}You resemble the girl\NI can't stop thinking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.77,0:02:12.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:129776,132654}{\i1}The girl Asuka Jr. likes…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.65,0:02:14.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:132654,134489}{\i1}The one he likes…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.48,0:02:16.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:134489,136282}Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.32,0:02:20.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:137325,140078}Oh, Meimi! Class is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.07,0:02:22.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:140078,142080}You were like that\Nthroughout the class.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.08,0:02:25.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:142080,145583}That's why the Sister was angry\Nand gave only you homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.58,0:02:27.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:145583,147251}Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.00,0:02:32.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:148002,152674}{\i1}But Asuka Jr.'s words\Nkeep repeating in my head…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.25,0:02:36.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:153257,156344}I've got an idea! Asuka Jr.!\NWhy don't you help her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.34,0:02:38.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:156344,158638}You can finish it\Nin 15 minutes, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.39,0:02:45.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:164394,165603}Don't be absurd!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.60,0:02:48.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:165603,168022}It's worthless unless\Nyou do it by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.02,0:02:50.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:169023,170900}They're going to start up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.90,0:02:52.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:170900,172276}That's all right, Ryoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.27,0:02:53.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:172276,173486}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.77,0:02:55.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:173778,175071}I'll do it by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.07,0:02:56.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:175071,176948}– What.?\N– The fight didn't start?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.11,0:03:03.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:180118,183121}You resemble the girl\NI can't stop thinking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.57,0:03:05.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:183579,185581}{\i1}Why did I say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.58,0:03:07.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:185581,187583}Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.33,0:03:12.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:188334,192588}You know the crown of the sun,\Nthe Prominence Crown, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.58,0:03:16.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:192588,196551}Yeah. It's showing\Nat the F Art Museum, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.55,0:03:19.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:196551,199262}Don't you think\NSt. Tail is going to target it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.18,0:03:22.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:201180,202473}What? What are you\Ntalking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.80,0:03:27.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:203808,207353}There's a treasure\Nlying at the end of the rainbow…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.27,0:03:29.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:208271,209897}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.89,0:03:34.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:209897,214193}The Prominence Crown was owned\Nby the Astoria Royal Family.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.19,0:03:36.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:214193,216404}These are the words\Nfrom the Royal Family's crest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.40,0:03:42.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:216404,222702}There are seven jewels on this crown which\Nare said to be from the end of a rainbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.95,0:03:44.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:222952,224245}Garnet…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.24,0:03:45.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:224245,225413}Topaz…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.41,0:03:47.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:225413,227832}Emerald and sapphire…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.83,0:03:49.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:227832,229667}They are seven colored jewels.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.66,0:03:50.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:229667,230877}How cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.37,0:03:56.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:231377,236966}But the ruby in the center has been missing\Nfor some time. It's a famous story.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.96,0:03:58.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:236966,238801}Some say it was stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.80,0:04:01.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:238801,241220}But no one knows\Nexactly what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.76,0:04:05.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:241763,245767}However! The ruby has resurfaced\Nafter over a ten-year absence.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.76,0:04:07.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:245767,247810}I've heard it will go on auction.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.10,0:04:10.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:248102,250938}How would it be possible\Nfor St. Tail to pass it up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.93,0:04:13.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:250938,253399}I've got the front-page article!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.39,0:04:15.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:253399,255359}You did good research.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.77,0:04:18.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:255777,258654}I've seen the crown.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.65,0:04:21.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:258654,261157}Wow! I should go to see it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.15,0:04:22.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:261157,262074}Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:25.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:263201,265912}{\i1}Unfortunately St. Tail has\Nno intention of stealing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.91,0:04:27.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:265912,267538}{\i1}Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.79,0:04:31.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:269791,271042}Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.25,0:04:33.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:271250,273711}Meimi's father!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.71,0:04:37.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:273711,277757}Thank you for being\Na good friend to Meimi, Seira.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.75,0:04:39.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:277757,279675}Not at all. The feeling is mutual.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.46,0:04:42.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:280468,282220}Today I came here to pray.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.22,0:04:44.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:282220,284430}What?\NIs something troubling you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.43,0:04:45.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:284430,285515}As a matter of fact…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.47,0:04:50.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:287475,290937}The other day, all three of us\Nwent to the F Art Museum.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.02,0:04:58.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:292021,298736}But since we saw the Prominence Crown,\NEimi, my wife, has been a little strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.32,0:05:00.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:299320,300947}She seems depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.99,0:05:06.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:302990,306452}What can I do to cheer her up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.45,0:05:07.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:306452,307370}Let's pray!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.74,0:05:10.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:307745,310706}I'm sure God will help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.66,0:05:14.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:312667,314585}Thank you, Seira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.88,0:05:23.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:321884,323594}I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.59,0:05:26.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:323594,326931}As I suspected, since that day\NMom has been depressed…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.93,0:05:29.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:326931,329267}You, too, are depressed…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.26,0:05:31.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:329267,331519}Your father said so\Nand is worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.51,0:05:33.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:331519,333813}Oh, I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.81,0:05:34.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:333813,334897}See?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.64,0:05:37.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:335648,337984}Enough about me.\NI'll ask Mom to her face!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.98,0:05:39.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:337984,339277}Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.98,0:05:41.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:339986,341863}Meimi…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.70,0:05:47.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:346701,347785}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.24,0:05:49.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:348244,349996}Mom, tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.99,0:05:54.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:349996,354876}Does the reason you're depressed have\Nanything to do with the Prominence Crown?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.29,0:06:01.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:360298,361966}Thank you, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.96,0:06:03.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:361966,363175}You've noticed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.21,0:06:05.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:364218,365803}You're right…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.80,0:06:08.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:365803,368180}Maybe it's about time\Nfor me to talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.36,0:06:23.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:382361,383321}Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.32,0:06:25.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:383321,385990}You know I was once\Na mysterious thief, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.99,0:06:27.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:385990,387158}Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.15,0:06:31.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:388159,391245}It was in a town very far from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.45,0:06:35.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:392455,395249}I was called\N"Mysterious Thief Lucifer".
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.24,0:06:37.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:395249,397001}It meant a devil\Nthat had fallen from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.21,0:06:47.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:405217,407845}I was a mean thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.51,0:06:54.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:408512,414810}I stole things from innocent people time\Nafter time and became the talk of the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.06,0:06:58.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:415061,418314}Did you say you wanted me\Nto walk in your footsteps?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.31,0:06:59.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:418314,419815}Oh, no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.81,0:07:02.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:419815,422902}The thing I want you to take\Nis my athletic ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.81,0:07:06.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:423819,426280}You don't do bad things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.28,0:07:07.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:426280,427740}I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.79,0:07:20.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:438793,440169}Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.16,0:07:24.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:440169,444382}Originally I started to do it\Nto test my athletic ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.46,0:07:30.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:445466,450346}But later I discovered that\NI couldn't stop being a thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.59,0:07:31.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:450596,451847}For what reason?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.84,0:07:34.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:451847,454183}Did you have someone who\Npursued you with all of his heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.18,0:07:36.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:454183,456894}– What?\N– Oh, nothing! Nothing at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.56,0:07:45.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:463567,465778}My rival showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.32,0:07:48.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:466320,468698}I still get irritated\Nwhen I think about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.69,0:07:52.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:468698,472201}A despicable mysterious\Nfemale thief showed up in the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.91,0:07:55.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:472910,475079}She enjoyed doing things for spite.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.07,0:07:57.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:475079,477039}She targeted whatever item\NI was planning to take.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.03,0:07:58.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:477039,478791}She was like a snake!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:02.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:479583,482670}Oh, Mom.\NYou're so competitive!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.29,0:08:05.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:483295,485131}But one night…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.72,0:08:15.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:491721,495307}While I was trying to get away from the police,\NI hurt my ankle because of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.39,0:08:19.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:497393,499979}I was in a desperate situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.94,0:08:26.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:502940,506068}Then someone hid me\Nwithout any questions…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.06,0:08:27.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:506068,507153}It was Dad, wasn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.57,0:08:34.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:510573,514452}He was living in a small apartment\Nand training to be a magician.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.82,0:08:36.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:514827,516912}I don't have it.\NWhat should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.70,0:08:40.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:517705,520041}I'm poor and I don't\Nhave any medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.04,0:08:41.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:520041,521375}It hurts, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.37,0:08:42.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:521375,522918}It's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.91,0:08:44.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:522918,524253}But don't make so much noise!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.92,0:08:46.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:524920,526756}If they find me, you'll regret it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.75,0:08:48.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:526756,528174}Oh, I've got an idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.17,0:08:49.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:528174,529717}Hey! Are you listening to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.42,0:08:51.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:530426,531343}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.34,0:08:52.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:531343,532303}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.30,0:08:53.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:532303,533471}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.56,0:09:04.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:542563,544440}I can only do something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.44,0:09:07.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:544440,547026}But it's good for hiding, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.03,0:09:19.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:558037,559747}Since then…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.74,0:09:23.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:559747,563209}Whenever we met,\Nhe gave me an armful of flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.20,0:09:24.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:563209,564335}Only flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.41,0:09:29.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:565419,569298}That's the only magic\Nhe could do at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.43,0:09:45.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:583437,585189}I was happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.27,0:09:51.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:586273,591570}Because he always did all he could\Nto try to make me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.15,0:09:58.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:592154,598494}When I watched him like that, I started\Nto think of the stupid things I had been doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.32,0:10:02.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:599328,602206}And I stopped being a thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:18.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:613384,618556}I planned on returning all of the things\NI had stolen to their rightful owners.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.55,0:10:20.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:618556,620975}At least I was planning to do so…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.76,0:10:27.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:621767,627064}But the one thing I couldn't return\Nwas the Prominence Crown's ruby.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.14,0:10:31.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:628149,631652}On the way to return it,\Nthat other woman took it from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.77,0:10:34.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:632778,634947}And that's how it ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.94,0:10:38.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:634947,638367}When I saw the crown,\NI remembered it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.86,0:10:40.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:638868,640661}Cheer up, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.66,0:10:42.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:640661,642204}I'm not going to tell Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.91,0:10:48.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:645916,648043}Dad knows everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.79,0:10:51.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:648794,651172}As always,\Nhe doesn't mention it to me.
Comment: 0,0:10:55.67,0:10:55.67,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:655676,655676}Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:11:00.68,0:11:00.68,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:660681,660681}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.14,0:11:05.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:661140,665519}Seira. I'm going\Nto get the Crown's ruby back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.51,0:11:10.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:665519,670149}The auction place\Nis the same as before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.14,0:11:13.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:670149,673611}So this time I don't think\Nyou should go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.61,0:11:17.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:673611,677448}Besides, I'm sure Asuka has\Nall of the information about the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.44,0:11:23.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:677448,683162}I've found the warehouse where\Nthey're keeping the ruby until the auction.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.09,0:11:37.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:696091,697259}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.67,0:11:38.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:697676,698594}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.42,0:11:40.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:699428,700888}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.09,0:11:47.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:702097,707311}"Tomorrow night, I'll take the Star Ruby\Nfrom the R Warehouse. – St. Tail"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.31,0:11:48.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:707311,708979}{\i1}St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.97,0:11:50.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:708979,710648}{\i1}As expected, she's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.85,0:11:55.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:712858,715736}{\i1}Asuka Jr. is in love\Nwith someone…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.07,0:12:00.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:718072,720282}{\i1}What should I do, Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.70,0:12:05.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:723702,725663}You haven't gone home yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.66,0:12:06.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:725663,726872}Neither have you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.96,0:12:13.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:730960,733295}Excuse me, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.63,0:12:24.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:739635,744598}Hello! I've just opened\Na fortune telling shop near this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.18,0:12:27.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:745182,747017}Please come by with your boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.14,0:12:31.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:749144,751063}Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.73,0:12:34.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:751730,754733}How cute! You're blushing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.06,0:12:38.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:755067,758696}Hello there! I've just opened\Na fortune telling shop…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.15,0:12:41.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:759154,761115}Please come!\NI'll be expecting you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.11,0:12:43.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:761115,763701}Hello, over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.70,0:12:46.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:763701,766662}I guess it's better\Nif you're not seen with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.45,0:12:50.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:768455,770124}I've never said that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.34,0:13:01.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:780342,781719}This is for your homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.71,0:13:04.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:781719,784305}You can peek only\Nif you can't figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.18,0:13:08.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:787182,788142}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.85,0:13:11.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:788851,791645}I didn't do it for your sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.52,0:13:13.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:792521,793981}Practice… practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.66,0:13:30.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:806660,810247}Oh, Lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.08,0:13:36.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:815085,816253}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.46,0:13:39.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:818464,819923}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.67,0:13:44.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:821675,824011}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.02,0:14:00.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:839026,840569}Good luck, Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.56,0:14:02.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:840569,842946}You can leave it to me!\NIt's for Mom and Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.07,0:14:08.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:845074,848869}May the blessings of God be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.09,0:14:27.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:866095,867179}There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.17,0:14:28.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:867179,868597}That must be the Star Ruby.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.39,0:14:31.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:869390,871308}Where is Asuka Jr.?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.22,0:14:36.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:874228,876730}{\i1}Today is the day I'll catch her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.23,0:14:38.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:877231,878148}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.14,0:14:38.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:878148,878941}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:40.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:878941,880275}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.73,0:14:45.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:884738,885948}Wait…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.94,0:14:48.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:885948,888283}It's too easy…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.28,0:14:49.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:888283,889868}Where is the security?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.12,0:14:58.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:893122,898585}The owner of the jewel refused\Nthe security in the warehouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.16,0:15:00.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:899169,900337}Are they outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.80,0:15:12.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:910806,912015}I've got her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.01,0:15:13.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:912015,913809}You won't escape today!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.80,0:15:14.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:913809,914768}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.76,0:15:15.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:914768,915561}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.56,0:15:16.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:915561,916687}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.85,0:15:23.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:919857,923944}I'm sorry, but you're the last\Nperson I want to catch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.83,0:15:36.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:934830,936290}At last I've found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.58,0:15:42.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:937583,942963}We've put the Star Ruby\Non auction to draw you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.96,0:15:44.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:942963,944423}The Mysterious Thief Lucifer…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.42,0:15:45.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:944423,945716}We've discovered\Nthe clue to finding you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.28,0:16:10.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:968280,970782}{\i1}You're the last person\NI want to catch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.20,0:16:15.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:974203,975287}I wonder…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.41,0:16:18.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:976413,978749}I wonder why I want to catch her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.45,0:16:22.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:980459,982711}{\i1}At first, I just wanted to catch her…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.79,0:16:26.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:983795,986673}{\i1}When you showed up, I was excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.04,0:16:28.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:987049,988175}{\i1}But then…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.92,0:16:30.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:988926,990677}{\i1}I didn't want\Nanyone else to have you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.26,0:16:41.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:999269,1001104}{\i1}From that moment on…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.71,0:18:32.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1109713,1112799}{\i1}There's a treasure lying\Nat the end of the rainbow…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.55,0:18:37.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1115552,1117429}{\i1}I don't remember\Nwhich royal family it was,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.47,0:18:39.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1117471,1119848}{\i1}but the end of the rainbow\Ncan't exist physically.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.64,0:18:42.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1120641,1122684}{\i1}Oh, shoot!\NI'll be late for school!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.23,0:19:32.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1168230,1172150}At the end of the rainbow,\Nthere is a treasure…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.82,0:19:38.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1176822,1178448}Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.44,0:19:41.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1178448,1181576}{\i1}Don't tell me he spent\Nthe whole night in the rain?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.24,0:19:44.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1183245,1184287}What's the matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.03,0:19:47.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1185038,1187416}What about you?\NIt's pretty early…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.41,0:19:48.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1187416,1188959}I'm on duty this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.95,0:19:50.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1188959,1190043}What happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.72,0:20:05.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1203724,1205225}You've got a high fever!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.22,0:20:08.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1205225,1208186}Wait a minute!\NI'll call your home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.18,0:20:09.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1208186,1209271}I love you…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.23,0:20:12.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1210230,1212149}I love you, Haneoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.56,0:20:15.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1213567,1215444}It's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.15,0:20:20.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1216153,1220907}I'm happy that you're here with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.87,0:20:31.87,saint tail sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:1227873,1231877}I am returning this. – St. Tail
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.50,0:20:35.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1232502,1235464}That my hand can reach you.
