Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.88,0:22:08.55,saint tail ed en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1325887,1328557}Let this sweet melody continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.55,0:22:13.43,saint tail ed en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1328557,1333436}Even if our love is shaken,
